{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345270/extras/logo-640x360.png?t=1730137649\" /><br><br>\u200b<br><br>Road to Hollow Hills thrusts players into a world where the line between reality and nightmare blurs. Engage in combat, solve puzzles, and explore a desolate world to unravel the enigma of Hollow Hills.<br><br>    Survival Horror: Navigate atmospheric environments filled with tension and dread.<br>    Dynamic Exploration: Roam through diverse locations, from the desolate National Park to the mysterious Shadowed Grove, uncovering the interconnected stories that shape Hollow Hills.<br>    Strategic Combat: Engage in visceral encounters with nightmarish creatures, utilizing a variety of weapons and tools. Manage stamina, choose your attacks wisely, and overcome relentless foes. Or try to avoid any combat!<br>    Puzzles: Solve challenging puzzles scattered throughout the world, each unlocking new areas and revealing secrets.<br>    Legacy System: Collect and utilize Legacy Tiers to enhance your attributes, uncover new abilities, and customize your character's strengths as you progress through the game.<br><br>Are you ready to face the nightmares that await on this haunting road?<br><br><i>Ride to survive, fight to win, Road... to Hollow Hills.</i>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345270/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730137649","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345270/page.bg.jpg?t=1730137649","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345270/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1730137649","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1345270/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1730137649","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"c